---
// Developmental Mentoring section
// Editorial/image-led layout with WHO/WHAT/HOW structure from brochure
---

<section id="mentoring" class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-brand-purple overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center" data-animate>
      <span class="text-brand-magenta font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">
        Career Growth
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.08] tracking-tight" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
        Developmental Mentoring
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-brand-magenta rounded-full mt-6 mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro with portrait and quote -->
    <div class="mt-16 lg:mt-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto" data-animate>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center lg:items-center">
        <!-- Portrait -->
        <div class="relative shrink-0 w-48 sm:w-56 lg:w-64">
          <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-brand-magenta/10 rounded-2xl -rotate-2"></div>
          <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-[3/4]">
            <img
              src="/images/brand/colin-keane-profile.png"
              alt="Colin Keane - Developmental Mentor"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-purple/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote only — centered vertically with portrait -->
        <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left">
          <blockquote class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed font-light italic">
            "I act as a trusted ally for those navigating big decisions, growing into leadership, or seeking clarity in their career direction."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-3 justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-0.5 bg-brand-magenta rounded-full"></div>
            <p class="text-white font-semibold">Colin Keane</p>
            <span class="text-white/50 text-sm">Founder & Principal Consultant</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Developmental Mentoring Matters -->
    <div class="mt-16 lg:mt-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto" data-animate>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="w-1 h-12 bg-brand-magenta rounded-full"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          Why Developmental Mentoring Matters
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-white/75 text-lg leading-relaxed pl-5 border-l-2 border-brand-magenta/30">
          I offer developmental mentoring to organizations with growing IT teams where professionals need guidance from someone with deep industry experience. Through regular support and mentorship, I help bridge capacity and knowledge gaps while fostering long-term professional growth.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/75 text-lg leading-relaxed pl-5 border-l-2 border-white/10">
          In today's hybrid working world, developmental mentoring is no longer a luxury—it's essential. For small IT teams, having access to an experienced external mentor alleviates capacity constraints while providing continuous guidance, constructive feedback, and a confidential space for professional growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Benefits -->
    <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6" data-animate>
      <!-- For the Learner -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-7 border border-brand-magenta/20 bg-brand-magenta/[0.04]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-brand-magenta/15 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-magenta" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-magenta tracking-tight" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
            For the Learner
          </h3>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Supportive learning environment</strong> with personalized guidance and a trusted space to grow</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Expert advice</strong> on technical challenges, interpersonal situations, and career decisions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Accelerated skill development</strong> in technical expertise and essential soft skills</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Fresh perspectives</strong> from an experienced ally who helps shape successful careers</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- For the Employer -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-7 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-tight" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
            For the Employer
          </h3>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Alleviate capacity constraints</strong> while ensuring continuous professional development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Independent feedback loop</strong> providing valuable performance insights</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Safe confidential space</strong> for challenges employees may not share with managers</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-magenta shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong class="text-white/90">Essential support structure</strong> in today's hybrid working environments</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Closing statement -->
    <div class="mt-14 lg:mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center" data-animate>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        The developmental mentor serves as a <strong class="text-white">supportive ally</strong>, offering valuable perspectives and constructive feedback to help learners navigate challenges and achieve sustained professional growth.
      </p>

      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-8 bg-brand-magenta text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(233,30,123,0.4)] hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Start the Conversation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
